{"agency_name": "Stafford Technologies", "website": "https://staffordtechnologies.net/?utm_source=gmb&utm_medium=referral", "domain": "staffordtechnologies.net", "city": "", "county": "Stafford", "state": "VA", "zip_code": "22554", "headcount": null, "headcount_source": "", "headcount_verified": false, "verify_status": "unverified_size", "source_notes": "places_census:digital marketing agency Stafford VA; maps=https://maps.google.com/?cid=3473958365645080805&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA", "places_id": "ChIJJUfbdirutokR5YjFTLr6NTA", "clutch_url": "", "linkedin_company_url": "", "employee_count_estimate": null, "vertical_focus": "", "pages": {"contact": "[fetch_failed: HTTP 404]", "about": "[fetch_failed: HTTP 404]", "portfolio": "Website Design &amp; Branding | Stafford Technologies Skip to content Services Showcase Website Starter Showcase Website Packages The Brand Schematic 4C Marketing Strategy Off The Ladder Services Showcase Website Starter Showcase Website Packages The Brand Schematic 4C Marketing Strategy Off The Ladder Start here... Branding &amp; Website Design Building Great Brands &amp; Websites Without the Bullsh*t. We help business owners showcase their business with a standout brand and website that turns website visitors into paying customers. Start here... Be Proud of Your Brand Attract the Right Customers Grow Your Business Is your website holding you back? Are you... pissed off because your website is losing you business? Are you... embarrassed because your website sucks? Are you... sick and tired of your brand making you look like an amateur? Stop losing to your competitors because of a stale brand and horrible website. Being in business is hard enough and you deserve better. It&#8217;s time for your brand and website to showcase your expertise and show the world you&#8217;re a badass at what you do, not an amateur. Start here... Standout Brands &amp; Websites Say goodbye to the same old same old and say hello to standing out! We&#8217;ll help you create a standout brand and website that showcases your expertise, and helps you stand out from the herd. Attract Better Prospects Who has time for tire kickers?! Attract the people you want to work with. Make More Money Attracting better prospects means more closed business. Stand Out Marketing Marketing is fun with a standout brand and website you're proud of. Done-for-you Solution Relax... We design it. We write it. We build it. We maintain it. Start here... The three ways we help you dominate your market... Whether you&#8217;re just starting out or you&#8217;re a seasoned business owner, Stafford Technologies has a website development package that fits your business. All of our branding and website solutions start with a success call to be sure we&#8217;re a great fit to help you grow your business, so click the button to get started and take the first step to leaving the same old same old behind. Start here... Starter Website If you're just starting out and want to plant your flag or your website is currently languishing in DIY purgatory, this is the perfect place to start growing your business. *This package is for small businesses with one main service. See how it works &gt;&gt; Showcase Website If you're ready to take your industry by the you-know-what and show the world you're the standout expert in your field, a Showcase Website will help you dominate your market. See how it works &gt;&gt; 4C Marketing Strategy You have a standout brand and a badass website - now it's time to scale in a big way. Use our 4C Marketing Strategy to launch your business to new heights. See how it works &gt;&gt; Stop losing and start growing... At Stafford Technologies, we&#8217;ve seen it happen over and over again: great businesses fall behind simply because they don’t have the know-how to build a memorable brand or an eye-catching website. They find it hard to compete and end up losing to competitors more often than not. That’s why we created the Showcase Website. Showcase Website packages give business owners the standout brand and website that sets them apart from the competition, turns more visitors into paying customers, and helps them dominate their market. With a kickass brand and a killer website, our customers are out there crushing it—growing their business, smashing their goals, and they&#8217;re fired up about their business&#8217; future again. Start here... Some of the great companies we work with... Stafford Technologies Contractor Websites Plus Contractor Websites Plus is a Stafford Technologies brand. Start here... 3 simple steps to building a standout brand and website... Step 1: Success Call Schedule a success call and let's choose the right package to help you reach your goals. Step 2: Plan &amp; Build We'll create the plan and build the standout brand and website you deserve. Step 3: Launch &amp; Win Launch your new website and start winning against your competition. Start here... \"The whole team at Contractor Websites Plus and Stafford Technologies were great to work with. The process was simple and the new brand and website are incredible. Thanks guys!\" Charlie Watts Affordable Garage Door Start here... \"The whole Stafford Technologies team was great to work with! I never felt rushed or pressured and they took so much time to understand what my goals were and how they can help plan and build a website that would support all of my branding and marketing. I could not have asked for a better experience!\" Molly Denham VEXA Services Start here... \"The discovery process was so incredible. I learned so much about my business and what it would really take to reach my goals. Michael and his team are the best in the business. If you need a new website there is no one I would recommend but Stafford Technologies.\" Andrea Sanfiorenzo-Delaney Sanfio Designs Start here... More Google 5-Star Reviews \"Our company has been working with Stafford Technologies for many years starting with the design of our website to an SEO campaign to years later a website redesign. As a small business having a website for contractors truly helps guide our customers to our products and services. We have been exceptionally pleased with their level of service, professionalism, and willingness to go the extra mile. We truly appreciate all that Stafford Technologies does!\" Troy Simonar CTW Wells & Pumps Mike and his team were great to work with for our website build. They took the time to find out what we wanted and needed and made it come to life. James Roberson 516 Project They really put their heart and soul into this and the website turned out amazing. Our previous website was kind of very hit or miss and not as detailed. With the new website Michael and his team did it is something to be proud of. Mike King Rays Siding & Exteriors I’ve been working with Stafford Technologies since 2017. They are a company who can guide you through the process and beyond. I love the fact that I can just call Michael anytime I need anything, and he always takes care of it for me. Their customer service is great. I am very happy with the results and I would recommend them to anyone trying to build a website. I am honored to be able to express my deep gratitude for their expertise. Jessica Scruggs Stormwater Great job by the staff of ST for developing and launching our non-profit Woodbridge Pickleball Club website. ST was professional, competent and best of all very patient with their novice website customers. Michael and Patricia are awesome people to work with and their entire staff is website knowledgeable, professional, friendly and helpful. I will definitely use them for future work. Great job, great website, thank you Stafford Technologies!!! DW Bartree Woodbridge Pickleball Michael and Patricia Pollaci have been amazing to work with! They are true professionals and have increased our Google Business Profile views over 200%. I highly recommend using their services for anyone looking to build up their business. Kathy Tate Loan Officer - Retired Working with Michael and Patty on our website was one of the best decisions we’ve made. Beyond getting a well-designed website (that included status updates of their progress throughout the project), we’ve received fantastic service even once the project was complete. Michael’s entire team is a pleasure to work with -- knowledgeable, efficient, and always on top of every task! If we could give more than a 5-star rating, we would! Steve Hilton Stafford County Historical Society After being told by another marketing company that the delay in getting my agency's Google My Business (GMB) page published was due to Google, Michael with Stafford Technologies set it up in a matter of days! I then hired Stafford Technologies to guide me and handle my GMB account and create a new website. I'm so grateful I found them! Victoria Nichols Professional Edge Cleaning Start here... What makes Stafford Technologies different from other website agencies? Most website agencies jump straight into design your website without understanding your business. At Stafford Technologies, we start with strategy because a great-looking site that doesn’t convert is just wasted money. We created the Brand Schematic to give business owners a clear plan for their website, brand, and marketing before the first pixel is placed. Our process ensures your website performs, not just exists. With over 300 websites launched, and every one custom-built (no templates, no fluff), we’re known for being strategic, bold, and relentlessly customer-focused. What is the Brand Schematic, and why do I need one? The Brand Schematic is our signature strategic discovery service. It’s a 2-hour deep dive into your goals, audience, message, and competition. Think of it like hiring an architect before building a house, you wouldn’t start construction without blueprints. For $695, you’ll walk away with a full roadmap for your brand, website, and marketing. Even better: if you choose to build your site with us, that cost is credited toward your project. It’s the smartest way to start any serious web presence and no other agency offers anything like it. How long does it take to build a Stafford Technologies website? It depends on the package. Our Showcase Starter websites are typically completed within 14 business days after your content interview. These are ideal for solo service providers or small teams with a single core offering. Our more advanced Showcase packages—Boost, Elevate, and Dominate—take approximately 4 to 6 weeks from final content approval. The timeline includes strategic planning, copywriting, SEO setup, and custom design. We prioritize quality and speed without sacrificing clarity or performance. Do I have to use Stafford Technologies to build my site after the Brand Schematic? Nope. The Brand Schematic is yours to keep. You’re under no obligation to continue with us, and we never block your exit. If you want to use another developer or build it yourself, you’ll still walk away with a professionally written plan. That said, nearly 100% of our Brand Schematic clients choose to stay with us because the clarity and trust built during the process make us the obvious next step. What’s included in your website packages? All our Showcase Websites are custom-built to support service-based businesses, and every package includes the essentials: clear messaging, mobile responsiveness, custom WordPress design (no templates), lightning-fast performance, basic SEO, and a stress-free launch. Our higher-tier packages—Boost, Elevate, and Dominate—include additional services like strategic content interviews, brand messaging, lead magnet creation, onboarding workflows, and even marketing funnels. You get exactly what you need to grow, without paying for fluff you don’t. Can you help me get found on Google? Yes and no. No. We do not possess a magic bullet that will get you on page one of Google. In fact, if anyone ever promises you that run &#8211; as fast as you can &#8211; the other way. Yes in that every website includes foundational Search Engine Optimization (SEO) baked in including fast load speeds, keyword structure, meta descriptions, and technical SEO best practices. This gives you the foundation of a great website and provides the opportunity for you to show up on the Google if your marketing is just as strong. If you want more visibility and leads, our 4C Marketing Strategy offers fully managed, sprint-based campaigns. We focus on real results, not vanity metrics. From Google Business Profile optimization to local search dominance and content strategy, we’ll help you show up where your ideal customers are already searching. Do you offer marketing services after the website is live? Absolutely. A great website is just the beginning. Our 4C Plans provide full-scale digital marketing built for long-term growth. Instead of cookie-cutter campaigns, we use monthly sprints to adapt to what’s working. This includes SEO, social media, email marketing, PPC, and conversion optimization all under one predictable monthly plan. You get a dedicated team focused on moving the needle every single month. How do I get started with Stafford Technologies? It all starts with a Success Call. This isn’t a sales pitch. It’s a no-pressure consultation where we learn about your business, your goals, and whether we’re a good fit for each other. From there, we may recommend a Brand Schematic to map out your strategy and guide you toward the Showcase package that’s right for your stage of growth. We believe small business owners should never feel confused, pressured, or oversold. Just click the button to schedule and we’ll take it from there. Start here... Click here to work ON your business instead of in your business&#8230; Brands &amp; Websites without the bullsh*t At Stafford Technologies, we know businesses without a great plan for their brand and website often struggle to stand out from the competi